 				By setting this option to "Make Public", you are agreeing to allow users to download the "Simple Export" format of your data. To mandate that users first ask your permission to download the data, you should set this option to "Require My Permission".<br/><br/>
 				
 				<%= f.radio_button "public_downloadable",false, {:class => "cbox",:selected=>true} %>Require My Permission (<em>User requests for download will be emailed to you</em>)<br/><br/>
 				<%= f.radio_button "public_downloadable",true, :class => "cbox" %>Make Public (<em>Registered users can download an Excel document representing the extracted data found in your project. All downloads will be recorded and viewed from your user profile.</em>)
 			</div><br/>
